divs: Sighting DetailsI don't know if this means anything but in 2007 Jan 11 I claim it was about 7:00 when I look north and then I see these white circle flat looking orb blueish Ufo's it had to be about 7-16 they were flying in formation as in a upside down triangle with the point facing east as if they were going back to Israel becasue I live in Florida and it's loacated east of Florida. Man I am still not sure to the fullest if I really seen them, I had a earge to go outside and look for Ufo's that day.
